ComicInfo.Series: Revenge of the Cosmic Ghost Rider
ComicInfo.Summary: Solar systems quake as the Cosmic Ghost Rider goes toe-to-toe with the mysterious head of the galaxy’s biggest crime syndicates! With nothing left to lose, will Cosmic Ghost Rider be able to come out on top or will his fire go out in a final brutal blaze of glory? Plus, all-new secrets of the Cosmic Ghost Rider’s origin revealed!
